StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetIRTAc.onDatesForCard]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@cardID uniqueidentifier
AS BEGIN
SELECT IRTAc.onDateID, IRTCardID, Ac.onDate, HoursSpent, TC, AC, HV, DC, ResultsAppt, ResultsIntv, RefReceived, MediaVisits, HSVisits, TOServiced, PooleeContacts, ContactVisits, LastUpdateDate, LastUpdateUser, EventID FROM IRTAc.onDatesRecap WHERE IRTCardID = @cardID ORDER BY LEFT(Ac.onDate,11) DESC
END
